20. A method according to embodiment 1 wherein the working device comprises a balloon catheter that has a flexible catheter shaft and a balloon on said catheter shaft.
21. A method according to embodiment 20 wherein the catheter shaft comprises at least one flexible region of flexural stiffness less than 200 pound-force per inch for a flexible region length of one inch.
